sql:
SELECT MAX(corporate_rate) AS max_corporate_rate
FROM corporate_taxes
WHERE country_id = 1 AND year_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "Corporate tax rate" refers to the percentage of profit a company is required to pay as tax to the government;
- "Digital services tax" is a tax levied on revenue from digital services provided in a country;
- "Tax incentive type" includes various forms of tax relief or benefits, such as R&D tax credits or digital services tax exemptions.

sql:
SELECT year, status
FROM tax_years
WHERE year = 2014;

external_knowledge:
